dispensary.name: Montana Kush - Helena
dispensary.description:
At Montana Kush our philosophy is that there's only one way to grow, which is through 100% natural cultivation. Many of our competitors prioritize volume thus running large operations which require a regular pesticide regiment. Here, we're different! We care about the medicinal quality of our plants above all else. We've found the best way to maximize the medicinal properties of cannabis is to keep grow rooms small so that each plant gets the individual attention it needs. We've always prioritized quality above all else, and that will never change.

Montana Kush is locally owned and operated in the Gallatin Valley of Southwest Montana. We live in a place that's perfect and pristine, and we plan on keeping it that way. We are both stewards of the land and protectors of our environment. These values are reflected in the way that we run our business and plan for the future.

We are also exceptionally proud that we employ local residents throughout the state of Montana. Our business would be nothing without our team, and we can't emphasize how fundamental they are in everything we do.So next time you're in the shop be sure to hug the budtender!

products.name: Buds | 41 G's
products.description:
41 G's is a captivating and potent cannabis strain that delivers a knockout punch of both flavor and effects. This indica-dominant hybrid, named after its impressive THC content, is a harmonious blend of genetics that promises a deep and immersive experience for cannabis enthusiasts.

Visually striking, 41 G's buds are a dense tapestry of deep green hues, accented by vibrant orange pistils and a generous coating of crystalline trichomes. The sheer resin production on these nugs attests to the strain's potency, inviting users into a world of relaxation and tranquility.

The aroma of 41 G's is a delightful fusion of earthy and sweet notes, with hints of pine and citrus that tickle the senses. Breaking open the buds releases an enticing fragrance that foreshadows the flavorful journey ahead.

Upon inhalation, the flavor profile of 41 G's unfolds, revealing a complex interplay of earthiness, citrus, and a subtle sweetness. The smooth and rich smoke or vapor makes for a pleasurable experience, setting the stage for the powerful effects that follow.

The high from 41 G's is a slow-building wave of relaxation that starts with a cerebral euphoria before cascading down the body, melting away tension and stress. The indica dominance ensures a profound sense of physical calm, making it an ideal choice for those seeking relief from insomnia, chronic pain, and muscle tension.

While 41 G's can be intense, its balanced effects make it suitable for both daytime and evening use, depending on personal tolerance levels. Medical users may appreciate its potential to alleviate conditions such as anxiety, depression, and appetite loss.

Whether you're a seasoned cannabis connoisseur or a newcomer to the world of strains, 41 G's invites you to experience a powerful and flavorful journey into relaxation and euphoria. Allow the profound effects of this strain to envelop you, offering a respite from the demands of the day and a chance to savor the essence of 41 G's.

products.name: Buds | Baby Yoda
products.strainDescription: Baby Yoda, also known as "Grogu", is an adorable hybrid weed strain made by crossing Khalifa Kush and The Menthol. Its buds are the bright, swampy green of Yoda himself or a green lightsaber, with orange hairs and abundant golden trichomes. The effects of Baby Yoda are believed to be sedating and tingly. Reviewers on Leafly say this weed strain makes them feel aroused, uplifted, and focused, but it won’t team you up with a Mandalorian. Baby Yoda has 24% THC. The dominant terpenes are myrcene and caryophyllene, which give off a diesel, tobacco-laced nose with sweet notes. Medical marijuana patients say they buy Baby Yoda for help with stress. The original breeder of Baby Yoda is Compound Genetics.

products.name: Buds | Apple Fritter
products.description:
Animal cookies x Sour Apple - 50-50 hybrid

Apple Fritter, a delectable hybrid born from the union of Animal Cookies and Sour Apple, is a cannabis strain that tantalizes the senses with its irresistible blend of flavors and effects. This harmonious combination results in a well-balanced experience that caters to both indica and sativa enthusiasts.

The visual appeal of Apple Fritter is nothing short of captivating, featuring dense and colorful buds adorned with an array of vibrant greens, deep purples, and fiery orange hairs. A generous layer of trichomes blankets the surface, hinting at the strain's potency and resinous nature.

True to its name, Apple Fritter boasts an aroma that mirrors the sweet and fruity essence of its parent strains. The scent is a delightful fusion of baked goods, with notes of crisp apples and a subtle undertone of earthiness. Breaking apart the buds releases a mouthwatering fragrance, setting the stage for the flavorful journey that awaits.

Upon consumption, the taste profile of Apple Fritter unfolds with a burst of sweetness, reminiscent of biting into a succulent apple pastry. The combination of fruity and dessert-like flavors makes each inhale a delightful experience, leaving a lingering, satisfying aftertaste.

The effects of Apple Fritter offer a well-rounded experience, combining the euphoria and mental uplift of sativa genetics with the relaxing and soothing qualities of indica lineage. Users may find themselves initially uplifted, with creative thoughts flowing freely, before gradually succumbing to a gentle physical relaxation that eases tension and stress.

Medical users appreciate Apple Fritter for its potential to alleviate symptoms of anxiety, depression, and chronic pain. Additionally, its balanced effects make it suitable for various occasions, whether it's a creative pursuit during the day or a relaxing evening unwind.

Apple Fritter invites cannabis enthusiasts to indulge in a sensory journey that marries the best traits of Animal Cookies and Sour Apple. Let the enticing flavors and well-balanced effects of this hybrid strain elevate your cannabis experience to new heights, offering a delectable escape into a world of sweet relaxation and creative inspiration.
products.strainDescription: Apple Fritter, a true hybrid weed strain, is known for its powerful and relaxing high. Put out by Lumpy’s Flowers, the Apple Fritter marijuana strain is a reported cross of Sour Apple and Animal Cookies. According to Leafly reviewers, Apple Fritter’s effects include feeling relaxed, giggly, and tingly. It's a great hybrid, combining the stone of GSC with the energy of a diesel. Apple Fritter cannabis has a flavor and aroma that come off as sweet and earthy, with a light, cheesy, apple pastry influence.

products.name: Buds | Kept Secret
products.description:
Kept Secret, a clandestine and alluring cannabis strain, lives up to its enigmatic name by delivering a uniquely captivating experience. The origins of this mysterious hybrid are closely guarded, adding an air of intrigue to its allure.

The buds of Kept Secret are visually striking, featuring a dense and resinous structure. A medley of deep greens and occasional purple hues, coupled with a generous layer of trichomes, creates an aesthetic that hints at the strain's concealed potency.

The aroma of Kept Secret is a complex bouquet, with subtle earthy undertones, hints of citrus, and a sweet, almost floral essence. Breaking apart the buds reveals a fragrant secret, inviting users into a world of sensory discovery.

Upon inhalation, the taste profile of Kept Secret unfolds in layers, with a harmonious blend of earthy notes and a delicate sweetness. The smooth and velvety smoke or vapor enhances the overall experience, leaving a lingering mystery on the palate.

The effects of Kept Secret are characterized by a well-balanced high, inducing a gentle euphoria and a sense of relaxation. This hybrid nature makes it versatile, suitable for both daytime and evening use, as it promotes a tranquil mental state without overwhelming sedation.

Medical users may find Kept Secret to be a discreet ally in managing symptoms of stress, anxiety, and mild pain. The strain's enigmatic effects contribute to its therapeutic appeal, offering a subtle yet effective escape.

Kept Secret beckons cannabis enthusiasts to uncover the mysteries within its buds and experience the allure of the unknown. Whether you're a seasoned explorer or a newcomer to the world of strains, this enigmatic hybrid encourages you to indulge in the clandestine charm of Kept Secret, where every session unravels a new facet of its intriguing nature.

products.name: Buds | Triangle Queen
products.strainDescription: The White is a potent hybrid marijuana strain known for having a distinct lack of odor or flavor. The White gives off a high that is usually described as providing equal body and head sensations. This mysterious strain—originally called “Triangle” and supposedly from somewhere in Florida—is aptly named. The White is covered with so many white trichomes that buds look like they were rolled in confectioner’s sugar. While it looks much like an OG in structure and certainly has the potency associated with the best OG Kush cuts, it has little of the smell or flavor found in those West Coast favorites. Those who do not enjoy the flavor and aroma of cannabis opt for this strain over more pungent varieties. Medical marijuana patients choose this strain to help relieve symptoms associated with insomnia.

products.name: Buds | Meltdown
products.strainDescription: Meltdown is an indica-dominant weed strain made from a genetic cross between The Cube and Orange Valley OG. Meltdown is 29% THC and 1% CBG, making this strain an ideal choice for very experienced cannabis consumers. Leafly customers tell us Meltdown effects include happy,  relaxation, and tingly. Medical marijuana patients often choose Meltdown when dealing with symptoms associated with depression, inflammation, and anxiety. Bred by the award-winning Exotic Genetix, Meltdown features flavors like cooling menthol, sour lime, and diesel. The dominant terpene of this strain is zesty limonene. The average price of Meltdown typically ranges from $12–$35. If you’ve smoked, dabbed, or consumed Meltdown, tell us about your experience by leaving a strain review.

products.name: Buds | Sour Tangie
products.strainDescription: Tangie, also known as "Sunva," is a popular sativa marijuana strain. Bred by DNA Genetics’ Sour Tangie is an 80% sativa cross between East Coast Sour Diesel and Tangie. Sour Tangie brings together the classic Sour Diesel aroma with Tangie’s creative, elevating buzz and strong citrus overtones. This sativa has two different phenotypes that express either Sour Diesel or Tangie bud structures and effects.

Strawberries & Cream invites cannabis enthusiasts to indulge in its rich flavors and experience the harmonious effects derived from its carefully selected parent strains. Whether seeking inspiration or a moment of tranquility, this hybrid strain encourages you to savor the delightful essence of Strawberries & Cream with each satisfying session.
products.strainDescription: Coming from Exotic Genetix, Strawberries and Cream crosses a Strawberry Jelly mother with a Cookies and Cream F2 male. A balanced hybrid, this strain produces strawberry flavors that will leave you asking for more. Thanks to the Cookies & Cream genetics, lime green buds are dense and resinous with hints of purple.

products.name: Buds  | Alaskan Thunderfuck
products.description: Alaskan Thunder Fuck (also referred to as ATF, Matanuska Thunder Fuck or Matanuska Tundra) is a legendary sativa marijuana strain originating in the Matanuska Valley area of Alaska. According to the legend, it was originally a Northern California sativa crossed with a Russian ruderalis, but sometime in the late 70s it was crossed with Afghani genetics to make it heartier. Alaskan Thunder Fuck usually presents large, beautifully frosted buds with incredibly strong odors of pine, lemon, menthol, and skunk. Known for possessing a relaxing yet intensely euphoric high, it is also described as having a “creeper” effect as well as pronounced appetite enhancement.
products.strainDescription: Alaskan Thunder Fuck (also referred to as ATF, Matanuska Thunder Fuck or Matanuska Tundra) is a legendary sativa marijuana strain originating in the Matanuska Valley area of Alaska. According to the legend, it was originally a Northern California sativa crossed with a Russian ruderalis, but sometime in the late 70s it was crossed with Afghani genetics to make it heartier (and also making it a hybrid). Alaskan Thunder Fuck usually presents large, beautifully frosted buds with incredibly strong odors of pine, lemon, menthol, and skunk. Known for possessing a relaxing yet intensely euphoric high, it is also described as having a “creeper” effect as well as pronounced appetite enhancement.

products.name: Buds | Lemon Head
products.description:
Lemon Head by Dark Horse Genetics

Bred by Dark Horse Genetics, Lemon Head is a double hit of lemon-inspired strains from a Lemonade female with a Lemon male. According to several online seed banks, the citrusy combination creates a sativa-leaning strain with extreme lemon flavor and a sour-yet-sweet taste.



Lemon Heads by Archive Seed Bank

A limited release from Archive Seed Bank, Lemon Heads is a cross of a Lemon G clone and Face Off. Lemon Heads yields big, resin-crusted buds that carry an intense lemon flavor. Lemon Heads appears to be discontinued.
Top reported effects, Relaxed, Euphoric, Happy.

products.name: Buds | Cherry Punch
products.strainDescription: Cherry Punch is a potent sativa-hybrid marijuana strain crossed between Cherry AK-47 and Purple Punch F2. Bred by Symbiotic Genetics, Cherry Punch (also known as Black Cherry Punch) is widely celebrated for its bold cherry flavor profile that comes from dense, citrus terpenes. Consumers who smoke this strain say it smells fruity and rich and a little skunk-like. The high you get from smoking Cherry Punch is uplifting and relaxing - perfect for jamming out to a new album or even taking care of a few errands. This strain is ideal for those seeking relief from anxiety and stress. Cherry Punch buds come in a dark green color with purple specks and striking orange hairs.

products.name: Buds | North Shore Maui
products.description:
North Shore Maui, a tropical and invigorating cannabis strain, takes its name from the scenic North Shore of Maui, Hawaii. This sativa-dominant hybrid is a fusion of Hawaiian and Afghani genetics, delivering a euphoric and uplifting experience reminiscent of the vibrant energy of the North Shore.

The buds of North Shore Maui are visually enchanting, featuring a dense and resinous structure with a spectrum of greens, accented by fiery orange pistils. The trichome coverage gives the buds a glistening quality, highlighting the strain's potency and resinous nature.

Upon inhalation, the taste profile of North Shore Maui unfolds with a symphony of fruity and floral notes, complemented by a subtle earthiness. The smooth and uplifting smoke or vapor enhances the overall experience, making each session a sensory journey inspired by the beauty of Maui's North Shore.

The effects of North Shore Maui are characterized by a euphoric and energizing high, inducing creativity and a sense of well-being. This sativa-dominant hybrid is suitable for daytime use, providing mental clarity and motivation without excessive sedation.

Medical users may find North Shore Maui beneficial for managing symptoms of depression, fatigue, and stress. The strain's mood-enhancing properties and energizing effects contribute to its therapeutic appeal.

North Shore Maui invites cannabis enthusiasts to bask in its tropical essence and embrace the spirit of the Hawaiian islands. Whether you're seeking inspiration or a mental escape, this sativa-dominant hybrid encourages you to ride the wave of euphoria and enjoy the uplifting experience of North Shore Maui with each delightful session.
products.strainDescription: North Shore Maui is a sativa-dominant weed strain made from a genetic cross between unknown Hawaiian strains. This strain is 70% sativa and 30% indica. North Shore Maui is a rare and tropical strain that delivers a light green buds with orange hairs and frosty trichomes. North Shore Maui has a musky and floral aroma with a fruity and floral aftertaste. North Shore Maui is 16-23% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers who enjoy a relaxing and cerebral high. Leafly customers tell us North Shore Maui effects include feeling happy, talkative, and creative. Medical marijuana patients often choose North Shore Maui when dealing with symptoms associated with stress, pain, and insomnia. Bred by unknown breeders, North Shore Maui features flavors like earthy, spicy, and citrus. The dominant terpene of this strain is myrcene, which is often associated with a fruity aroma and anti-inflammatory effects. The average price of North Shore Maui typically ranges from $30-$40 per eighth. North Shore Maui is perfect for a morning or daytime use as it will make you feel uplifted and energized without being too jittery. Some users have compared the high to a strong cup of coffee with a mellow sativa sensation. If you’ve smoked, dabbed, or consumed North Shore Maui, tell us about your experience by leaving a strain review on Leafly.

products.name: Buds | Blue Grapefruit
products.description:
Blue Grapefruit, a tantalizing cannabis strain, is a harmonious blend of Blueberry and Grapefruit genetics. This sativa-dominant hybrid offers a delightful sensory experience marked by a burst of fruity flavors and uplifting effects.

Visually, Blue Grapefruit captures attention with its vibrant and dense buds, showcasing a spectrum of greens punctuated by orange pistils. The trichome coverage gives the buds a frosty appearance, reflecting the strain's potency and resinous nature.

The aroma of Blue Grapefruit is a delightful fusion of sweet berries and citrus, creating an invigorating and refreshing olfactory experience. The zesty grapefruit notes intertwine with the sweet blueberry undertones, setting the stage for a flavor profile that mirrors its aromatic complexity.

Upon inhalation, the taste journey of Blue Grapefruit unfolds with a medley of sweet and tart notes, reminiscent of biting into a succulent grapefruit complemented by the subtle sweetness of blueberries. The smooth smoke or vapor enhances the overall experience, making it a pleasurable choice for cannabis enthusiasts.

The effects of Blue Grapefruit are characterized by a cerebral uplift and a surge of energy, making it an ideal strain for daytime use. Users may experience enhanced focus, creativity, and a general sense of euphoria without the heaviness often associated with indica-dominant strains.

Medical users may find Blue Grapefruit beneficial for managing symptoms of depression, fatigue, and stress. Its energizing effects can also provide relief from conditions that benefit from increased motivation and mental clarity.

Blue Grapefruit invites cannabis enthusiasts to embrace its vibrant and uplifting qualities. Whether you're seeking a boost in creativity or a mood-enhancing experience, let this sativa-dominant hybrid take you on a journey of fruity bliss and euphoria, offering a refreshing twist to your cannabis repertoire.

products.name: MoonRocket Infused Pre-Roll | Pineapple Express
products.strainDescription: Pineapple Express is a sativa-dominant hybrid marijuana strain made by crossing Trainwreck with Hawaiian. Pineapple Express produces long-lasting energetic effects that you can feel right away. Pineapple Express is 18% THC and may make you feel buzzy, alert, and creative. The best time to smoke Pineapple Express is in the morning, afternoon, or early evening hours. In terms of flavor, this strain packs a punch to your pallet with bright citrus notes infused with pineapple and earthy pine, thanks to the terpenes of caryophyllene limonene and Ocimene. Medical marijuana patients choose Pineapple Express to relieve symptoms associated with depression, pain, and fatigue. The average price per gram of Pineapple Express is $20.

products.name: Shatter | Baby Yoda | 1g
products.strainDescription: Baby Yoda, also known as "Grogu", is an adorable hybrid weed strain made by crossing Khalifa Kush and The Menthol. Its buds are the bright, swampy green of Yoda himself or a green lightsaber, with orange hairs and abundant golden trichomes. The effects of Baby Yoda are believed to be sedating and tingly. Reviewers on Leafly say this weed strain makes them feel aroused, uplifted, and focused, but it won’t team you up with a Mandalorian. Baby Yoda has 24% THC. The dominant terpenes are myrcene and caryophyllene, which give off a diesel, tobacco-laced nose with sweet notes. Medical marijuana patients say they buy Baby Yoda for help with stress. The original breeder of Baby Yoda is Compound Genetics.
